title: Tin Foil Hat #64: Vatican Secrets with Eleanor Kerrigan
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli! Today Ryan and Sam welcome from the The Comedy Store Podcast, Eleanor Kerrigan, to discuss secrets of the Vatican and the Roman Catholic Church. On this episode we discuss...
1)TREATY OF 1213​
2)The Vatican owns The Crown
3) The Jesuit movement
4) Adam Weishaupt and The Bavarian Illuminati
5) The Black Pope
6) Pope’s Audience Hall
Thank you for all of your support!
